tei:div.tei:p:
Many thanks for Buxbaum’s address;
        the printed score of my Fourth Quartet will be
        sent by the publisher directly to him.
        Additionally, it will be broadcast on the 25th of this
          month on Leipzig Radio. – From Vrieslander I finally received a letter from Locarno in which he describes the terrible state he is in;
        naturally, I will do whatever I can for him. –
